def do_linregress(vin, vout, vin_range):
    lower, higher = vin_range
    cond1 = vin > lower
    cond2 = vin < higher
    indices = [np.where((cond1) & (cond2))][0][0]
    vin = vin[indices]
    vout = vout[indices]
    res = linregress(vin, vout)
    return vin, vout, res
